import React from 'react';
import Navbar from './Navbar'

import NavItem from './NavItem'

import Container from './Container.js'

import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom'

class Play extends React.Component {
	render() { return (
		<Router>
	    <Container>
	    	<Navbar>
	    		<NavItems justify='center'>
	    			<NavItem href='#nowhere'>Stats</NavItem>
	    			<NavItem>RP</NavItem>
	    			<NavItem>Combat</NavItem>
	    			<NavItem>Bag</NavItem>
	    		</NavItems>
	    	</Navbar>
	    	<Container>

	    	</Container>
    	</Container>
    	</Router>		
	);}
}

export default Play;
